                    <span>Go and get a book called "tales from the time loop" by David Icke!  It covers all this and much more!  One of the best books to come around in decades...</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Too ambiguous....</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
